{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Jump into your next great adventure in this challenging, fun-filled 3D platformer!</strong></h2><br><br><strong>It\u2019s a disaster!</strong> Kit\u2019s sister Vixie has been kidnapped by Dregnor, Skyreach Mountain\u2019s resident dragon. And it\u2019s way too dangerous for anyone to go after them! \u2026Right?<br><br>Well, Kit\u2019s not the kind of fox to give up so easily. He\u2019s determined to confront the menacing dragon, even if that means going on the quest of a lifetime!<br><br>What awaits Kit on his perilous journey?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE!</strong></h2><br>Immerse yourself in a <strong>huge, interconnected world!</strong> Your adventure might take you anywhere\u2026<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> An abandoned mine deep underground?<br></li><li> Colourful treehouses high up in a forest canopy?<br></li><li> The flooded shrine to a water serpent?<br></li><li> An enchanted metalworks factory?<br></li><li> You name it!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017840/extras/Kit_s_Quest_Looping_Video_1__Walking___GIF_.gif?t=1706136081\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>COLLECT!</strong></h2><br>Scavenge everything you can get your paws on to help make headway on your quest!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Dregnor has placed magical barriers throughout the land\u2026 Look for <strong>dragon teeth</strong> and use their magic to break through!<br></li><li> Friendly birds might be willing to lend you a hand (or wing)\u2026 especially after you bribe them with some gathered <strong>berries</strong>!<br></li><li> Queen Nelli has lost her <strong>Golden Mushrooms</strong>! Find them and Her Majesty may reward you handsomely!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017840/extras/Kit_s_Quest_Looping_Video_2__Tooth___GIF_.gif?t=1706136081\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>OVERCOME CHALLENGES!</strong></h2><br>Confront all sorts of novel challenges, whether you need to\u2026<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make creative use of Kit\u2019s many <strong>cool abilities</strong>, from summoning ice block platforms out of thin air, to remotely detonating mushroom spore bombs!<br></li><li> Use your foxy cunning to <strong>solve tricky puzzles</strong>!<br></li><li> Put your <strong>platforming prowess</strong> to the test in a multitude of exciting environments!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017840/extras/Kit_s_Quest_Looping_Video_3__Challenges___GIF_.gif?t=1706136081\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIND FRIENDS!</strong></h2><br>Meet and befriend a marathoning parrot, a skittish bunny, a world-famous stork archaeologist, and many more allies who will help you on your way!  <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017840/extras/Kit_s_Quest_Looping_Video_4__NPCs___GIF_.gif?t=1706136081\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIND\u2026 FOES?</strong></h2><br>As if Dregnor wasn\u2019t bad enough by himself, his alliance with the deadly spiders who roam the land is sure to cause trouble. If you find yourself going up against a crystalline arachnid at least twenty times your size (and probably in a bad mood), just remember\u2026 Vixie\u2019s counting on you!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2017840/extras/Kit_s_Quest_Looping_Video_5__Bosses___GIF_.gif?t=1706136081\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>THE RIGHT CHALLENGE FOR EVERYONE!</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> With several <strong>difficulty options</strong>, Kit\u2019s Quest can be enjoyed by beginners and 3D platforming veterans alike!<br></li><li> There\u2019s also a dedicated <strong>Speedrunning mode</strong> for those who like to go fast.<br></li><li> Finally, there might just be s